snippet.title: KHYAAL RAKHYA KAR - Asim Riaz & Himanshi Khurana | Preetinder | Anshul Garg | Latest Punjabi Song
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Khyaal Rakhya Kar sung by Preetinder ft. Asim Riaz & Himanshi Khurana.

Listen Khyaal Rakhya Kar on streaming apps

Gaana- https://gaana.com/album/khyaal-rakhya-kar
Saavn- https://www.saavn.com/s/song/punjabi/Khayaal-Rakhya-Kar/Khayaal-Rakhya-Kar/AlBbdzd0dF0
Wynk - https://wynk.in/u/67Nw9fj5I 
Apple Music- https://music.apple.com/in/album/khayaal-rakhya-kar-single/1517776304

Singer : Preetinder 
Music : Rajat Nagpal
Lyrics: Babbu
Music Produced and Arranged by Rajat Nagpal 
Mastered by Rahul Sharma@AMV
Starring: Asim Riaz & Himanshi Khurana

Produced By: Anshul Garg

Video Director - GURINDER BAWA
Assistant Director - Preet Surrey
Editor - Gaurav K Mehra
Dop - Shinda Singh 
DI - Onkar Singh
Video Supervisor: Raghav Sharma
Project Manager : Piyush Chandak
Poster : Vicky Sandhu 
Distribution: Believe Digital  
Digital Promotions- Team DMF

Lyrics:


Time te roti kha
Time te saun ja
Time te gal kar
Time te milan aa
J raat nu jaanan bahr tan munde naal rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain Tu apna khayaal rakhya kar

Kade kade roti aake ghare vi tan khaya kar
Vaise jinna dil kare paise tu udaaya kar
Kade kade coke naal saar leya kar ve
Roz roz theek nahi peg ghatt laaya kar
Chote hi changey lagde chote vaal rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain Tu apna khayaal rakhya kar

Chakkar nahi koi jinna marzi tu jach ve
Duniya hai sarhdi tu nazran ton bach ve
Babbu meri gal sun kudiyan ton duur rahin
Hath torh dau j koi tenu karu touch ve
Tu cheez pyaari hain Aehnu sambhaal rakhya kar
Mera tu hi tu tan hain Tu apna khayaal rakhya kar

Rabb nu chaddin na fer bahut agge jaayenga
Main dekhya karangi jadon tv utte jaayenga


#Preetinder #AsimRiaz #HimanshiKhurana

snippet.title: Do Ka Chaar | Chaman Bahaar | Lyrical Video | Sonu Nigam | Jitendra Kumar, Ritika Badiani
snippet.description:
Chaman Bahaar streaming on Netflix from 19th June onwards!

Presenting the love song of the season - Do Ka Chaar with lyrics from the movie Chaman Bahaar. The track is sung by Sonu Nigam and composed by Anshuman Mukherjee. Chaman Bahaar stars Jitendra Kumar and Ritika Badiani in lead roles. The film is directed by Apurva Dhar Badgaiyann.

An ambitious young man, in a small town in Central India, sets up a paan shop to a floundering start. His fortunes start to change dramatically when a family shifts in the house across the road. Hordes of boys start following the teenage girl from the family and set up an 'adda' at Billu's shop. His business flourishes tremendously but Billu is now unhappy than ever, as he has fallen for the girl himself! 

Song credits

Singer - Sonu Nigam
Composed by Anshuman Mukherjee

An ambitious young man, in a small town in Central India, sets up a paan shop to a floundering start. His fortunes start to change dramatically when a family shifts in the house across the road. Hordes of boys start following the teenage girl from the family and set up an 'adda' at Billu's shop. His business flourishes tremendously but Billu is now unhappy than ever, as he has fallen for the girl himself!
